c: 2
v: 124
t: "Unibuke ubwo Nyagasani wa Aburahamu yamugeragereshaga amategeko, akayubahiriza. (Nyagasani) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri, ngiye kukugira umuyobozi w’abantu.” (Aburahamu) aravuga ati “No mu rubyaro rwanjye?” (Nyagasani) aravuga ati “(Ni byo, ariko) isezerano ryanjye ntirizagera ku nkozi z’ibibi.”"